{"tid":1054012,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普推翻奧巴馬規定 不再公佈無人機殺傷平民數字","createTime":"2019-03-09T13:52:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-09T15:05:57.000Z","uid":28765,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ba842c6f1fac510abf005a138a67646dda309634","tid":1054012,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T13:52:23.000Z","msg":"特朗普再次將奧巴馬所為還原。美國總統特朗普簽署行政命令，推翻前總統奧巴馬規定，讓中央情報局（CIA）不再公佈美軍無人機殺傷平民數字。美國國務院形容，美軍無人機殺傷平民報告「多餘」和「令人分心」。<br />\n<br />\n911恐怖襲擊後，美國興起使用無人機打擊恐怖組織目標，做法在阿富汗、巴基斯坦等國尤其盛行，這些無人機行動都由中情局負責執行，而多年來除了恐怖分子，有不少平民同樣死於美軍無人機打擊。<br />\n<br />\n美國前總統奧巴馬2016年簽令，要求中情局公佈無人機每年殺傷平民數字，特朗普現在則把規定廢除，只是美軍仍需遵守國會要求另作報告。國務院稱，特朗普廢除了多餘的報告要求，原本的規定無助提高透明度，反而令情報人員從主要工作分心。<br />\n<br />\n非牟利調查新聞機構Bureau of Investigative Journalism指，美軍自2004年以來，執行逾6,700次無人機打擊任務，估計錯殺最多超過1,700名平民，當中包括約250至400名兒童。<br />\n<br />\n數據亦顯示，特朗普執政兩年來，美軍共發動超過2,200次無人機打擊，數字比奧巴馬執政8年的1,878次還多一截。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://wealth.hket.com/article/2287859/%E3%80%90%E7%BE%8E%E8%BB%8D%E7%84%A1%E4%BA%BA%E6%A9%9F%E3%80%91%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E6%8E%A8%E7%BF%BB%E5%A5%A7%E5%B7%B4%E9%A6%AC%E8%A6%8F%E5%AE%9A%20%E4%B8%8D%E5%86%8D%E5%85%AC%E4%BD%88%E7%84%A1%E4%BA%BA%E6%A9%9F%E6%AE%BA%E5%82%B7%E5%B9%B3%E6%B0%91%E6%95%B8%E5%AD%97\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwealth.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2287859%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%25BB%258D%25E7%2584%25A1%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25A9%259F%25E3%2580%2591%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25E6%258E%25A8%25E7%25BF%25BB%25E5%25A5%25A7%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E8%25A6%258F%25E5%25AE%259A%2520%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2586%258D%25E5%2585%25AC%25E4%25BD%2588%25E7%2584%25A1%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E5%2582%25B7%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%2595%25B8%25E5%25AD%2597&d=hArt0m4UYatnQvENVNvF2Ag0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=ea829ba2\" target=\"_blank\">https://wealth.hket.com/article/2287859/%E3%80%90%E7%BE%8E%E8%BB%8D%E7%84%A1%E4%BA%BA%E6%A9%9F%E3%80%91%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E6%8E%A8%E7%BF%BB%E5%A5%A7%E5%B7%B4%E9%A6%AC%E8%A6%8F%E5%AE%9A%20%E4%B8%8D%E5%86%8D%E5%85%AC%E4%BD%88%E7%84%A1%E4%BA%BA%E6%A9%9F%E6%AE%BA%E5%82%B7%E5%B9%B3%E6%B0%91%E6%95%B8%E5%AD%97</a>"},{"pid":"997f57bc3aa1f3185bec868399467b82dff43449","tid":1054012,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T13:53:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14a1c496d4b45c0db70e6d414f40be433af33e46","tid":1054012,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T13:54:24.000Z","msg":"快刀斬亂麻好過拖拖拉拉"},{"pid":"b23dbbf36c1bb2bb3b7c8d2fae1499900bb72939","tid":1054012,"uid":164266,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T14:31:35.000Z","msg":"講真 中東人命真係唔值錢"},{"pid":"175a8b7da3409d86914bfc3c2a21c33cfac7033e","tid":1054012,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T15:05:57.000Z","msg":"中東班生翻算9數啦"}]}